        <abstract> 
<p>Praises MS of first chapter of HWB’s book [<hi rend="italic">The naturalist on the river Amazons</hi> (1863)]. Suggests he give common names and make comparisons to familiar English species to help readers. Suggests a few changes. Will speak strongly to Murray about publishing whenever HWB is ready.</p> 
        </abstract>
